Last modified on Mon 9 Dec 2019 11.57 GMT Streaming really came into its own in the 2010s – even though it actually wasn’t until 2017 that streaming revenues overtook both physical sales and digital downloads. We’ve rummaged through Spotify’s data to discover who among the incredible artists below has been the most popular on Spotify with UK users over the past 10 years. Can you guess who the top streamers are? Spotify has unlocked 10 years of streaming history to commemorate the end of the 2010s. Check out your decade in music and relive the songs that meant something to you here. All data provided directly by Spotify, and is accurate up to 12 November.